message:
We extend our deepest condolences to the families, friends, and colleagues of Special Agents Daniel Alfin and Laura Schwartzenberger.  Praying for the injured agents.
We are continually thankful for the bravery of law enforcement who work tirelessly to protect our children.  #Heroes
